# Line endings: store and check out as LF on every platform.
#
# This repository is a one-way mirror, regenerated from a Windows
# monorepo whose exported files use LF. Without an explicit rule a
# Windows checkout (core.autocrlf) rewrites every file to CRLF and the
# whole tree then shows as modified against the next LF re-export.
# Pinning LF keeps the working tree byte-identical to the export
# everywhere, so a re-export is a clean diff instead of churn.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Raw binary test fixture (MathType MTEF bytes) — never convert.
*.bin binary
